@startuml Fig_3_4_3_DFD_Inference_Story_Generation
title Fig 3.4.3: Data Flow — Inference / Story Generation Phase\n(generate.py / server.py + SLM.generate)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

package "User / UI" {
  actor "User prompt\n(text)" as U
}

package "Encoding" {
  rectangle "**tiktoken**\nGPT-2 BPE" as ENC
  entity "Prompt token IDs\n(≤ block_size)" as IDS
}
U --> ENC : encode_ordinary
ENC --> IDS

package "Checkpoint" {
  storage "**best.pt**\nmodel_state + config" as CKPT
  rectangle "**SLM** loaded\n**.eval()**" as MODEL
}
CKPT --> MODEL

package "Autoregressive loop" {
  rectangle "**Prime KV caches**\nfeed prompt tokens\none-by-one" as PRIME
  rectangle "Repeat up to **max_new_tokens**" as LOOP
  rectangle "**norm_f** + **lm_head**\n(last position logits)" as HEAD
  rectangle "**temperature**, **top-k**\n**softmax** → **multinomial**" as SAMPLE
  entity "Next token ID" as NEXT
}
IDS --> PRIME
MODEL <-- PRIME : tok_emb + pos_emb\nper layer **kv_cache**
PRIME --> LOOP
LOOP --> HEAD
HEAD --> SAMPLE
SAMPLE --> NEXT
NEXT --> LOOP : append; extend caches
NEXT --> ENC : decode for display

package "Stopping" {
  rectangle "Stop on **eos_token**\nor context full" as STOP
}
NEXT --> STOP

ENC --> U : full story string

note right of PRIME
  Inference uses **KV-cache**\nper layer; after prompt,\n**is_causal=False** for new query
end note

@enduml
